and splicing the N image feature vectors with the text feature vectors in sequence respectively, wherein one row or one column of the multi-mode feature vectors comprises one image feature vector and the text feature vector.
With reference to the first aspect, in another possible implementation manner, the text to be processed includes a plurality of texts, the feature is extracted from the text to be processed to obtain text feature vectors, and the method further includes respectively extracting the features from the plurality of texts to obtain a plurality of text feature vectors, wherein the text feature vectors are in one-to-one correspondence with the texts;
